民爱国运动的旧法令，颁布革命的新法令。释放一切爱国的革命的政治犯，开放党禁。全国人民动员起来武装起来，参加抗战，实行有力出力，有钱出钱，有枪出枪，有知识出知识。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"642dadd68b","type":"paragraph","text":"五、抗日的外交政策：","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"687316b939","type":"title","text":"中国共产党抗日救国十大纲领","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6eec2f3680","type":"paragraph","text":"对日绝交，驱逐日本官吏，逮捕日本侦探，接收日本帝国主义在华财产，否认日本外债，废除日本条约，收回日本租界。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ad8a3cae6","type":"paragraph","text":"财政政策以有钱出钱及没收汉奸财产作抗日经费为原则，经济政策是整顿与扩大国防生产，发展农村经济，保证战时农产品的自给，提倡国货改良土产，禁绝日货，取缔奸商，反对投机操纵。","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"813eb7775a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、打倒日本帝国主义：","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8564d384b4","type":"paragraph","text":"改变教育的旧制度旧课程，实行以抗日救国为目标的新制度新课程。","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88ccb240c6","type":"paragraph","text":"国防政府执行抗日救国的革命政策。实行地方自治，铲除贪官污吏，建立廉洁政府。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8913934290","type":"paragraph","text":"动员蒙民回民及其他一切少数民族，在民族自决和民族自治的原则下，共同抗日。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ac191ff4b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全国军事的总动员：","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94f3fe2947","type":"paragraph","text":"实施普及的义务的免费的教育方案，提高人民民族觉悟的程度。","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0318cf9db","type":"paragraph","text":"《解放杂志》","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36